::Feline::

She smiled at the compliment.  She sat at her work bench and got 
things organized. She still had to find two other bots to put them 
into.  Then she remebered Iron Raptor talking of two injureed bots 
that might come in. She smiled and put the chips away.  She waited 
for HotRod to get out and then she would go to the mess hall and ge 
herself something to eat.
